            <fr:taxon>Corollary</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>The set of strings over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left \{(,),a,b,\ldots ,z\right \}\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> in which parentheses are well-nested is not <fr:link href="jms-017Y.xml" title="Regular language" addr="jms-017Y" type="local">regular</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
